<h2>Mouth sores, Sore tongue, Swollen tongue and White patches on tongue</h2>
<p>WebMD Symptom Checker helps you find the most common medical conditions indicated by the symptoms mouth sores, sore tongue, swollen tongue and white patches on tongue including Thermal burn of mouth or tongue, Drug allergy, and Allergic reaction.</p>
<p>There  are 16 conditions  associated with mouth sores, sore tongue, swollen tongue and white patches on tongue. The links below will provide you with more detailed information on these medical conditions from the WebMD Symptom Checker and help provide a better understanding of causes and treatment of these related conditions.</p>
